.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Sport: tennis, skateboarding, soccer, parkour, snowboarding
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Birthday: february, april, january, june, november
1. Sport:tennis == Color:red
2. Sport:swedish == Birthday:january
3. Sport:skateboarding == Beverage:tea
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Birthday:april
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Sport:parkour is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Birthday:february
11. Birthday:novembers is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Beverage:beer
13. Sport:soccer == Cigar:prince
14. Sport:parkour is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
